{"tid":2006034,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"5**題目考考你（自認maths唔差嘅入）","createTime":"2020-05-07T13:26:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T17:52:56.000Z","uid":199716,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"4d8195bad8d1339ac6e4d339ed546400edc4a378","tid":2006034,"uid":199716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:26:45.000Z","msg":"今日返工要做quiz, 突然諗起一條題目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有一個Quiz, 得5條題目 全部都係MC可以選擇a, b, c ,d <br />\n份quiz嘅passing rate 係 80%或以上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過fail左可以無限次再做過<br />\n<br />\n咁當你宜家決定純粹靠randomly亂撞答題目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要你係3次attempt或以內就pass 份quiz 嘅機會率係幾多？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：我自己都未諗到答案 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82eb8c55bc1bc937294d52140182cb9b6509be5c","tid":2006034,"uid":208196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:28:35.000Z","msg":"我諗Lv 4都識？"},{"pid":"50bb5be55e0951cfb0739e9c80f38a371320e4ee","tid":2006034,"uid":199716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"82eb8c55bc1bc937294d52140182cb9b6509be5c","tid":2006034,"uid":208196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:28:35.000Z","msg":"我諗Lv 4都識？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:29:18.000Z","msg":"好似差咁啲嘢...答案呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7b7676f618ac0bb40760ccedf474e9efe8588a3","tid":2006034,"uid":194109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:30:14.000Z","msg":"咁底智數學題"},{"pid":"7daa0f6acc5752921c303a09df829d62e4974477","tid":2006034,"uid":98022,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:32:41.000Z","msg":"～99%"},{"pid":"74761acea72b73469935cff00a09c35b947e751e