/>\n<br />\n其實去到呢到就做唔到，因為你冇估幾多次既中既distribution 係follow咩distribution,最簡單我當normal,你又冇比mean 同sd<br />\n<br />\n例如啲人平均估10次，sd係3<br />\n<br />\n你要既答案就係反查normal由負無限去到3 呢面積=0.0098乘0.015<br />\n=1.44*10^-4"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:44:56.000Z","msg":"Sor無加埋全中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5894844d5cf1d037c3a5bf5eb596eabf6e2d485","tid":2006034,"uid":50428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:52:12.000Z","msg":"如果好似master mind每次都會講岩錯/對到答案又唔同玩法<br />\n我上面個計法係wild guess 到永遠最後先出結論"},{"pid":"a731c3771eabb1c3bd03f9645efe5db9fdd469ed","tid":2006034,"uid":41243,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T14:21:59.000Z","msg":"合格分8成就係0.046<br />\n合格率8成就視乎個分數係咩distribution"},{"pid":"409b848121a33e009a77580683866736fc620e42","tid":2006034,"uid":21514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T14:41:49.000Z","msg":"0.0461"},{"pid":"7c5b26c492e395508e94690109cb13fe9a57598d","tid":2006034,"uid":43373,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T15:15:57.000Z","msg":"50%<br />\n因為只有合格同唔合格呢兩個可能性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca698328391ee716626b05b811a2973d748d1995","tid":2006034,"uid":2771,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"409b848121a33e009a77580683866736fc620e42","tid":2006034,"uid":21514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T14:41:49.000Z","msg":"0.0461"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T17:07:03.000Z","msg":"Agreed.<br />\n<br />\nLet x = P(4 or 5 correct) =<br />\n5C4 * 0.25^4 * 0.75 + 0.25^5<br />\n<br />\nAnswer = x + (1-x) * x + (1-x)^2 * x = 0.046146392<br />\n其實即係抽波抽到中爲止<br />\ndse無教名但要你諗到的Geometric distribution<br />\n但 p 要你自己計"},{"pid":"c8f6db7190549bf43f36f29bc938d8152b3ae713","tid":2006034,"uid":15636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T17:40:59.000Z","msg":"中四程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n0.25^4 * 0.75 * 5 + 0.25^5<br />\n最後寫埋啲可能性出黎加晒佢咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n機都費事㩒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af37251b9afa896e5f5c44fc0cc2bc87ce31c243","tid":2006034,"uid":278847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:28:25.000Z","msg":"1<br />\nIt's because p(pass)=5C4*0.25^4*0.75+5C5*0.25^5=0.015625.<br />\nThe required probability=p+(1-p)*p+(1-p)^2+...=p(1-0)/(1-(1-p))=p*1/p=1."},{"pid":"55fb8b6685a88622136505c379a081be620693d6","tid":2006034,"uid":201890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:27:01.000Z","msg":"correct rate for each question =1/4<br />\ncorrect rate for 5 questions =（1/4）^5<br />\ncorrect rate for 4 questions = 5C4 x （1/4）^4<br />\n<br />\npass rate = ［（1/4）^5 + 5C4 x （1/4）^4］x3<br />\n                 = 63 / 1024 =0.0615<br />\n<br />\n3 means 3 times of attempt"},{"pid":"7e2267bce9a957fb2b1c763ded4e27cebd8f5352","tid":2006034,"uid":280516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"594f5376892338544c3bd0d9aa33e275a99cf15d","tid":2006034,"uid":50428,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T13:43:57.000Z","msg":"P(any 4Q correct)<br />\n5C4* 0.25^4*0.75<br />\n=0.015<br />\n<br />\n其實去到呢到就做唔到，因為你冇估幾多次既中既distribution 係follow咩distribution,最簡單我當normal,你又冇比mean 同sd<br />\n<br />\n例如啲人平均估10次，sd係3<br />\n<br />\n你要既答案就係反查normal由負無限去到3 呢面積=0.0098乘0.015<br />\n=1.44*10^-4"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:32:38.000Z","msg":"用geometric distribution<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26471e37248e430b3554e352b5e587dea40d2cdb","tid":2006034,"uid":274542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:38:10.000Z","msg":"第一次過：20%<br />\n第一次唔過第二次過：80%*20%<br />\n第一二次唔過第三次過：80%*80%*20%<br />\n加埋：48.8%"},{"pid":"426d664ea884962c077f53806e5ce1dbd3f9d95b","tid":2006034,"uid":274542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26471e37248e430b3554e352b5e587dea40d2cdb","tid":2006034,"uid":274542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:38:10.000Z","msg":"第一次過：20%<br />\n第一次唔過第二次過：80%*20%<br />\n第一二次唔過第三次過：80%*80%*20%<br />\n加埋：48.8%"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T17:52:56.000Z","msg":"sor睇錯咗<br />\n<br />\npass要啱4題或5題<br />\n啱4題：5 * 25%^4 * 0.75 <br />\n啱5題：25%^5<br />\n加埋= 1.5625%%<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一次就pass: 1.5625%<br />\n第一次fail第二次pass: 98.4375% * 1.5625%<br />\n第一二次fail第三次pass: 98.4375%^2 * 1.5625%<br />\n加埋=4.6146%"}]}